window.bookSummaryJSON = "Steve is a man for today. He was born in Oklahoma in the 50s and grew up thinking that the world was a wonderful place. Just like the Cleavers, he thought that everyone in the whole USA was like the people in his neighborhood - honest, hard working, God-fearing people.<p>Then he started traveling around the country. Boy, was he wrong!</p><p><b>For Adults Only: Explicit language. Must be 18 years of age to purchase.</b></p>"; 
